<section class="card">

    <h2>Demi Human</h2>

    <p>
        Fierce, cunning, and remarkably adaptable, Demi Humans survive through
        agility and instinct. Though smaller than most races, they make up for
        their stature with ferocity, stealth, and relentless aggression in battle.
    </p>

</section>

<section class="card">

    <h2>Race Traits</h2>

    <table>
        <tr>
            <th>Trait</th>
            <th>Details</th>
        </tr>

        <tr>
            <td>Ability Score Increase</td>
            <td>Dexterity +2, Strength +1</td>
        </tr>

        <tr>
            <td>Age</td>
            <td>Reach maturity within a few years and live roughly half as long as humans.</td>
        </tr>

        <tr>
            <td>Size</td>
            <td>Small</td>
        </tr>

        <tr>
            <td>Speed</td>
            <td>30 feet</td>
        </tr>

        <tr>
            <td>Darkvision</td>
            <td>60 feet</td>
        </tr>

        <tr>
            <td>Languages</td>
            <td>Common and Demi-Human</td>
        </tr>

    </table>

</section>

<section class="card">

    <h2>Darkvision</h2>

    <p>
        You can see in dim light within 60 feet as if it were bright light,
        and in darkness as if it were dim light. You cannot discern color in
        darkness, only shades of gray.
    </p>

</section>

<section class="card">

    <h2>Rampage</h2>

    <p>
        When you reduce a creature to 0 hit points with a melee attack on your
        turn, you can take a bonus action to move up to half your speed and
        make another melee attack.
    </p>

</section>

<section class="card">

    <h2>Nimble Escape</h2>

    <p>
        You can take the Disengage or Hide action as a bonus action on each of
        your turns.
    </p>

</section>

<section class="card">

    <h2>Stealthy</h2>

    <p>
        You gain proficiency in the Stealth skill.
    </p>

</section>

